<!--Exercise 3 - Test Catalog

* A laboratory wants to safe his experiments
* The list should contain the title of the experiment, the duration, the price,
  the person doing the test, a tool list with short descriptions of the tools and the used number
* The saved file should also include the day on which it was saved
* Create the general structure of this XML file with the corresponding tags and attributes
* Write down the details for at least two experiments-->

